1
00:00:15,759 --> 00:00:16,440
Madam,

2
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:19,039
do you recognize this man?

3
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:25,960
Lady Yin,

4
00:00:26,559 --> 00:00:27,559
why would you think

5
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:29,079
I would recognize such a criminal?

6
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:31,160
Because he is the one who killed your husband,

7
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,159
and also the one who framed my father.

8
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:33,840
What...

9
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:34,840
What?

10
00:00:35,079 --> 00:00:35,560
Speak up!

11
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:36,240
It's...

12
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,079
It's her!

13
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:38,560
She promised me gold and silver

14
00:00:38,799 --> 00:00:40,399
to attack the Yin and Xiao caravans.

15
00:00:40,799 --> 00:00:42,759
She also asked me to leave

16
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,039
the Yin family's token at the scene

17
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,960
to draw attention to Yin Shifeng.

18
00:00:46,399 --> 00:00:47,640
She also said that after the job was done,

19
00:00:47,799 --> 00:00:48,079
I would

20
00:00:48,359 --> 00:00:49,880
take over the Xiao family's trade route.

21
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,280
Shut up!

22
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,159
You shameless bandit!

23
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,560
You're slinging lies!

24
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:54,719
No.

25
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,479
Every word I said is true.

26
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,479
I'm not lying.

27
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,159
You appear kind and benevolent,

28
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:01,960
but in reality,

29
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,039
you're as cold-hearted as a snake.

30
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,120
To get Xiao family's property,

31
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,040
you colluded with bandits,

32
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:09,319
to kill my husband,

33
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,560
frame others,

34
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,439
and twist the truth,

35
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:13,879
pushing our family into a dire situation!

36
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:14,400
Enough!

37
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,519
You're talking nonsense!

38
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:17,719
I...

39
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:21,000
I loved my husband dearly,

40
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:23,799
and I treated Yunzhou as my own.

41
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:26,719
If you hadn't been out all day,

42
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,159
how could I not accept you?

43
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:32,560
I'll pretend

44
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,599
this never happened.

45
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:35,760
But don't

46
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,359
bring it up again.

47
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,920
You want to go?

48
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:52,799
If you hadn't threatened me with the treaty,

49
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:53,920
I wouldn't be in this mess!

50
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:55,280
It's all your fault!

51
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:58,040
You made me trick the caravans to Panyu.

52
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,280
And you

53
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,799
had me forge the treaty for the Ministry of Revenue.

54
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,879
You even used Yin Shifeng

55
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,400
as your shield.

56
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,920
You treacherous woman,

57
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,680
you want to kill me to silence me.

58
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,080
If I can't live,

59
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,560
neither can you!

60
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,360
Guards,

61
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,919
take Lady Liu back to her room.

62
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,520
Are you planning to save her?

63
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,919
The secret meeting hasn't been cleared up yet.

64
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,080
If she dies,

65
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,199
the clues will be lost.

66
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:27,639
Fine,

67
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,159
then go ahead.

68
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,280
I'm here.

69
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:34,759
Nong,

70
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,719
take Shen Yuan to the supreme court.

71
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,520
She lost too much blood,

72
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:50,960
but her life is not in danger.

73
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,159
She needs rest.

74
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,439
The secret meeting is still unclear.

75
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,680
Send her to the Supreme Court in a few days,

76
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:01,120
and the truth will come to light.

77
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:05,319
Good and evil will eventually be rewarded.

78
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:07,240
It's just a matter of time.

79
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,759
You must be tired after a night of work.

80
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:13,159
Go back and rest.

81
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:14,879
I've already sent someone

82
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,080
to guard the door.

83
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,439
It seems that Sun has been searched

84
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:23,120
throughout the whole mansion.

85
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,520
She must have fled

86
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,719
once her crimes were exposed.

87
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,439
Father,

88
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:37,360
Qingdai and I have come to see you.

89
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,800
Now that the truth has come to light,

90
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,520
you don't need to worry about the Xiao Family anymore.

91
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,199
I will ensure that no one

92
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,240
can take advantage of us again.

93
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,840
That's right, Uncle Xiao.

94
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,439
Now,

95
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:54,360
Yunzhou has grown into a

96
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,039
composed and capable young master

97
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,240
who can handle things on his own.

98
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,719
He even deceived me.

99
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,879
What are you thinking about?

100
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,360
I'm thinking...

101
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,639
Are you suspecting the Liu family?

102
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,000
They also have a caravan.

103
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,000
Before my father passed away,

104
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,439
he warned me to be cautious,

105
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,240
but he didn't get a chance to explain.

106
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,639
Now that I think about it,

107
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,439
it might be her.

108
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,759
Then,

109
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,040
we might as well

110
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,160
give it a try.

111
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,879
If she knows

112
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,319
that there's a rift between us,

113
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,480
she would be eager to

114
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,720
take advantage of the situation.

115
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,720
You and I,

116
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,319
let's part ways

117
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,839
and go our separate ways.

118
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,279
Fine,

119
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,360
as you wish.

120
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:11,279
You can either do your job

121
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:13,040
and I won't shortchange you,

122
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,480
or...

123
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,959
I've had a drink tonight,

124
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:23,000
so I might not control my strength well.

125
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,439
You know, in this prison,

126
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:26,959
it's not uncommon for guards

127
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,639
to get hurt while handling

128
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,399
isn't it?

129
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,279
Am I right?

130
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:35,839
Yes,

131
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:36,879
of course.

132
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,160
If you need anything,

133
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,199
just let me know.

134
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,199
Why didn't you deliver the medicine yourself?

135
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,160
It's not the right time yet.

136
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,759
The prison is not a clean place.

137
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:54,800
A single mistake

138
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:57,240
could alert the enemy.

139
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,480
We should take our time.

140
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:02,319
Once we have concrete evidence,

141
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:04,480
we can take decisive action.

142
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,160
I wonder,

143
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,079
how will you repay me?

144
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,079
What do you mean by that?

145
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:19,279
I haven't even settled the score with you yet!

146
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:20,079
Do you know

147
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,759
how many tears I shed in that prison?

148
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:21,199
Let's

149
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,240
get married.

150
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:36,319
Dad,

151
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:37,680
your daughter-in-law

152
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,319
seems to be shy.

153
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,199
I'm not.

154
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:44,079
Didn't we agree to go

155
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:45,920
visit the Grand Secretariat?

156
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,199
Let's go.

157
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,959
Hurry up.

158
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,480
I invited you here today

159
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,040
to share some good news.

160
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,240
The secret agreement

161
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,199
has been found.

162
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,959
It details

163
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,199
their profit-sharing ratio,

164
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,680
responsibilities,

165
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,920
and even

166
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,560
the time

167
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:05,240
and location of the handover.

168
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,120
Shen Yuan is responsible

169
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,720
for inspecting and pricing the goods,

170
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:09,279
and issue official documents

171
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:11,199
to exempt the tax on the goods.

172
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,839
Su Erman was responsible for providing goods,

173
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,160
providing various resources

174
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,800
from Persia.

175
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:15,879
The transportation

176
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,879
was handled by the Liu family.

177
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:20,759
Yin Shifeng was on the contract to the Ministry of Revenue.

178
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,160
In case one day

179
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,920
I found something suspicious,

180
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,920
the Liu family could also distance themselves from the matter.

181
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,240
This secret agreement

182
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,480
has been hidden

183
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,800
in the hands of the military officer of the Judicial Council.

184
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,800
He is the elder brother of the Liu family.

185
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,079
No wonder.

186
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,480
Don't take the same path as your father.

187
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,079
I should have thought of it earlier.

188
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,639
He is also involved.

189
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,319
Ms Yin, rest assured.

190
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,800
Now the Supreme Court

191
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,079
has obtained concrete evidence.

192
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:48,160
None of them will escape.

193
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,600
I implore you, my lord,

194
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,199
to reveal the truth to the world

195
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,120
and restore justice.

196
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,040
That is a given.

197
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,920
Thank you, my lord,

198
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,040
for clearing my father's name.

199
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:05,160
I should be thanking you both.

200
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,920
Without your

201
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,920
joint efforts,

202
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:11,439
the truth would never have come to light.

203
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,160
My lord,

204
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:16,519
I have another request

205
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,519
to make.

206
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,759
I hope you will grant it.

207
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,079
Go ahead.

208
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,759
The successful investigation

209
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,199
of the trade issue

210
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:27,160
was not just the work of the two of us.

211
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:30,600
The two ladies from the Women's Clinic

212
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,800
also played a crucial role.

213
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,039
One of them is from the Ming Yue Pavilion.

214
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,759
Now that her master is dead,

215
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,480
I wish to seek freedom for her.

216
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:41,759
With no master and having performed a service,

217
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:45,759
I will certainly strive for her freedom papers.

218
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,320
Thank you, my lord.

219
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:58,759
Sir!

220
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:00,000
Sir!

221
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:00,879
Someone...

222
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:01,759
Someone died!

223
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,639
There are two bandits over there who have killed someone.

224
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:04,919
Please go and check.

225
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,639
I'll go with him.

226
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:08,320
You two take them to the prison.

227
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:08,759
Yes.

228
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:09,440
This way.

229
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:09,639
Go.

230
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:10,320
This way.

231
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:10,639
Go.

232
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,399
Sir.

233
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:20,840
Go.

234
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:23,960
Sign it.

235
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:27,080
From now on, we are no longer a couple,

236
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,720
and have nothing to do with each other.

237
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:31,279
Divorce?

238
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,559
You wish!

239
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,080
As long as I don't divorce,

240
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:41,159
you are a dog of the Shen Family,

241
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:42,720
and will never be free of it.

242
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,679
This slap

243
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,120
is for your corruption,

244
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,240
and murder for money.

245
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,120
How dare you!

246
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,080
This slap

247
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,120
is for your ungratefulness

248
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,639
and betrayal.

249
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:03,200
Do you think

250
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,559
I'm a pushover?

251
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,080
You've taken advantage of my love

252
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,000
and forgiveness.

253
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,440
Don't forget,

254
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:16,840
my family controls the trade routes.

255
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,399
This divorce paper

256
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:21,200
means nothing to me.

257
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:22,799
Yi.

258
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,399
My Lady.

259
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,720
This hairpin

260
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,120
was made by me for you.

261
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:31,679
Yunzhou.

262
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:33,559
Seven years ago,

263
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,200
I broke my promise at Qujiang Pool.

264
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,320
Let bygones

265
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,080
be bygones.

266
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:39,320
Qingdai,

267
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,120
will you be my wife?

268
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,080
Will you?

269
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,639
Are you just saying this on a whim?

270
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,399
No,

271
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:52,840
I've been planning this for a long time.

272
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:54,679
Over the years,

273
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,080
we've had our disagreements,

274
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:57,720
and I've harbored resentment towards you.

275
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,879
But those feelings have long turned to regret

276
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,440
every time I lingered outside your mansion.

277
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,440
I keep thinking,

278
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,960
if I had been more resolute,

279
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,360
if I had trusted you more,

280
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:08,840
we wouldn't

281
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,799
have missed these seven years.

282
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,200
Qingdai,

283
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,279
after the mourning period,

284
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,519
will you marry me?

285
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:24,120
If you ever break my heart,

286
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:26,120
I...

287
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:29,759
I swear by the ancestors of the Xiao family,

288
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:31,919
[I swear,]

289
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:33,799
[you are the only one for me.]

290
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,799
[We'll be together forever.]

291
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,679
[I'll never betray you.]

292
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,759
Step into the flames,

293
00:12:29,519 --> 00:12:31,120
vanquish all evil.

294
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:36,919
Purify with clear spring,

295
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,120
from now on,

296
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,480
all will be peaceful.

297
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,799
[Welcome back.]

298
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,080
We must make this Women's Clinic

299
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,279
even better.

300
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,320
Why are there so many patients these days?

301
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,000
The medicine stock is not enough.

302
00:13:36,639 --> 00:13:38,480
Go and replenish these missing medicines.

303
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:39,440
Don't delay.

304
00:13:39,879 --> 00:13:40,279
Yes.

305
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:48,320
Let me take your pulse first.

306
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:49,480
Okay.

307
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,919
Did it suddenly become like this,

308
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,279
or did it gradually worsen?

309
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:57,919
The pulse is floating, slippery and chaotic.

310
00:13:58,879 --> 00:13:59,799
It's not a normal cold.

311
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,600
Is there anyone else in your family with similar symptoms?

312
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:03,639
Come on.

313
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,000
A bit of fever.

314
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:09,399
Have you vomited?

315
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:10,840
Yes.

316
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:14,600
Alright.

317
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:15,639
Come on.

318
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,000
Ma Xing Shi Gan Decoction.

319
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:31,399
Wait a moment.

320
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:35,759
Keep distance from your family these days.

321
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,759
All utensils must be boiled in water.

322
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:39,840
Right.

323
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,000
Clothes

324
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,559
and bedding should be often exposed to the sun.

325
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:45,039
If you find your symptoms getting worse,

326
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:46,320
come to us in time.

327
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,639
What's going on?

328
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,759
In the past two days, there have been

329
00:15:05,759 --> 00:15:06,759
dozens of people with similar symptoms.

330
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:08,279
fever,

331
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:09,159
abdominal pain,

332
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,559
severe diarrhea,

333
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,799
and bloody vomit and stool.

334
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,320
It's not just a common cold.

335
00:15:15,919 --> 00:15:16,639
I'm afraid

336
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,519
an epidemic is coming.

337
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,559
Sister Su,

338
00:15:24,519 --> 00:15:25,679
prepare more common herbs.

339
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:26,559
Okay.

340
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:31,799
Come on.

341
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,039
Make some

342
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,720
preventive medicine

343
00:15:36,559 --> 00:15:37,960
and distribute it to the healthy.

344
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:39,000
Okay.

345
00:15:49,519 --> 00:15:50,559
What happened to you?

346
00:15:52,559 --> 00:15:54,000
I'm not sure.

347
00:15:54,639 --> 00:15:57,519
I just drank some water,

348
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,720
and my belly suddenly hurt so much.

349
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,919
Is this water from the river?

350
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,519
Yes.
